        <div class="welcome__description">
          <p>
            To our patients and their families - We are here to meet your Healthcare Needs.
          </p>
          <p>
            While how we work has changed during this pandemic, what we do has not. Our motto is to put you our
            patients
            first and design how we work around you.
          </p>
          <p>
            So when you visit us in person, we will be wearing PPE. We have made some changes - clinical workflows,
