            To minimise risk, we are asking patients who do not have an appointment to not come to the surgery. If you
            have ANY symptoms of coronavirus, do not come to the surgery.
          </p>
          <p>
            Call us for routine queries, or fill in this form for repeat prescription or social welfare certificate
            requests, or this form to request a non-urgent telephone or video consultation.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any respiratory symptoms (cough, shortness of breath) or fever do not attend.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www2.hse.ie/coronavirus" target="_blank" class="button corona-btn">Find out more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
